  ---
  Pagination guide

  Both catalogs use the same pagination shape:

  {
    "data": [...],
    "total": 20257,
    "take": 10,
    "skip": 0,
    "nextCursor": "uuid"
  }

  Skip/take — use for known page numbers:
  ?take=10&skip=0   → page 1
  ?take=10&skip=10  → page 2

  Cursor — use for infinite scroll / load-more (more efficient):
  ?take=10                        → first page, get nextCursor from response
  ?take=10&cursor=<nextCursor>    → next page
  When nextCursor is null, you are on the last page.